</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>【報價】Samsung Galaxy S21 FE 5G 輕旗艦機，香港行貨價錢 + 規格 + 現場試相</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/01/04/samsung-galaxy-s21-fe-5g/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=samsung-galaxy-s21-fe-5g</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jan 2022 10:22:16 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[手提電話]]></category><category><![CDATA[Galaxy S21]]></category><category><![CDATA[samsung]]></category><category><![CDATA[Samsung Galaxy S21 FE 5G]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1079527</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Samsung 為 Galaxy S21 智能電話系列加入了新產品 Galaxy S21 FE 5G。新機集合 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Samsung 為 Galaxy S21 智能電話系列加入了新產品 Galaxy S21 FE 5G。新機集合了 S21 眾多功能與繼承了經典外型設計，同樣提供高性能 Snapdragon 888 處理晶片組，流暢的 120Hz 熒幕，並以莫迪蘭色系的 4 種顏色給用家選擇，包括有炭灰黑、橄欖綠、丁香紫、陶瓷白。<a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0015.jpg"><br /></a></p><p><a title="20211201_192925" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/51798995854/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/51798995854_5d4dcd0d09_b.jpg" alt="20211201_192925" width="1024" height="768" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br />▲攝自 Galaxy S21 FE 5G, 可點擊進入 flickr 相簿放大或下載原圖，內文下部有其他試相！<br /><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0023.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1079528" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0023-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0023-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0023-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0023.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0018.jpg"><br /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0022.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1079530" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0022-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0022-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0022-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0022.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0038.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1079531" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0038-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0038-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0038-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0038.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0004.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1079534" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0004-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0004-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0004-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0004.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0008.jpg"><br /></a></p><p>Samsung Galaxy S21 FE 5G 擁有繼承了 S21 強大功能與設計，其輪廓切割的鏡頭組合邊框，令手機背面看上去更加簡潔。炭灰黑、橄欖綠、丁香紫、陶瓷白四種色彩的機身使用了霧面機背設計，機身厚度只有 7.9 毫米，可輕鬆放入口袋中。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0044.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1079546" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0044-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0044-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0044-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0044.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>性能方面，Galaxy S21 FE 5G 搭載了 Snapdragon 888 Octa-Core 晶片，香港上市的配置包括有 8GB RAM+256GB ROM 以及 8GB RAM+128GB ROM（此配置只提供炭灰黑，並只限於 Samsung 網上商店、三星專門店有售）。原生已搭載有 Android 12 作業系統，6.4 吋 Full HD++<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span>Dynamic AMOLED 2X 熒幕更新率達到 120Hz。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0008.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1079535" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0008-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0008-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0008-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0008.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0010.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1079536" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0010-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0010-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0010-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0010.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>S21 FE 5G 同樣有 3 鏡頭設計，後置鏡頭組包括有超廣角 12MP(f2.2)、廣角 12MP 配備 Dual Pixel 及光學防手震 (f1.8)，以及一個混合式光學變焦 3x 的 8MP 感光元件、配備光學防手震的遠攝鏡頭 (f2.4)，支援極黑亮攝、30x 極遠變焦攝影功能。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0040.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1079543" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0040-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0040-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0040-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0040.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0041.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1079544" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0041-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0041-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0041-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0041.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0043.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1079545" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0043-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0043-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0043-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0043.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲1x，10x，30x 相機拍攝功能示範</p><p>機內配置有 4,500 mAh 大電池，支援 25W 超快速充電，能夠在 30 分鐘由 0% 充電至 50% 以上。手機支援 5G 流動網絡。 其 IPX8 防水功能允許短暫抵抗 1.5 米水深中浸沒 30 分鐘。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0018.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1079529 size-large" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0018-506x900.jpg" alt="" width="506" height="900" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0018-506x900.jpg 506w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0018-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0018-768x1365.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0018-864x1536.jpg 864w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0018-1152x2048.jpg 1152w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0018.jpg 900w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 506px" /></a></p><h2>供貨日期及建議零售價</h2><p>Samsung Galaxy S21 FE 5G 即日起開始預售，並於 1 月 11 日正式公開發售，用家可以 HK$598 加購 Samsung Care+ 兩年保障。</p><p>型號：Galaxy S21 FE 5G, 8GB RAM+256GB ROM</p><p>顏色：炭灰黑、橄欖綠、丁香紫、陶瓷白</p><p>售價：HK$5,598</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0032.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1079532" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0032-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0032-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0032-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0032.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>型號：Galaxy S21 FE 5G, 8GB RAM+128GB ROM</p><p>顏色：炭灰黑</p><p>售價：HK$5,198</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0026.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1079539" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0026-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0026-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0026-7